{"tid":2142191,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"反駁內地專家 醫管局：深喉檢驗一樣好","createTime":"2020-08-06T08:44:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T10:37:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f04430f8274ea941395e21a1ef98de807d92a290","tid":2142191,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T08:44:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200806/7HQXQUTIARU7R5OCET6QOKPSMA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200806%2F7HQXQUTIARU7R5OCET6QOKPSMA%2F&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOvilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=06792856\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200806%2F7HQXQUTIARU7R5OCET6QOKPSMA%2F&h=aee3489e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200806/7HQXQUTIARU7R5OCET6QOKPSMA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n反駁內地專家 醫管局：深喉檢驗一樣好<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TtkwLDt8HIEiuq88MxKXensl8HI=/190x128/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3KB6SB4D5TGYZSGB2BSVEAUJ6M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTtkwLDt8HIEiuq88MxKXensl8HI%3D%2F190x128%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3KB6SB4D5TGYZSGB2BSVEAUJ6M.jpg&h=ccb9f46f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】「內地核酸檢測支援隊」隊長豪言要提升本地檢測量到10多萬至20萬個，有報道更指支援隊內有專家質疑亞博館的病毒檢測方法太粗糙，建議亞博醫護應抽取病患的鼻咽拭子樣本檢驗，醫管局總行政經理劉家獻昨在疫情記者會上回應時表示，深喉唾液檢測對病毒的敏感度與鼻咽拭子檢測差不多，甚至更高，「香港專家研究過，發現兩種檢測敏感度一樣咁好」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：400呎住15人 床貼床衞生差<br />\n<br />\n混合檢測或睇漏病毒量低患者<br />\n<br />\n劉指日後醫管局會盡量以深喉唾液檢測，使更多市民更簡單地做檢測；他補充，在檢測鼻咽拭子時，對周遭環境上較有限制，例如在取樣本時，要空氣流通，協助的醫護亦要穿全套保護衣，而深喉唾液檢測則較為簡單。<br />\n<br />\n本身是醫務化驗師的醫管局。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"19b56584bfa4083a03baaa85e75bf557fcf3fac1","tid":2142191,"uid":65638,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T08:46:17.000Z","msg":"會唔會犯國安法<br />\n區區醫管局憑咩反對中央嘅專家？"},{"pid":"3043365dd9a4a6308e983f20e9ca18c0ccf4888e","tid":2142191,"uid":46906,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T08:47:22.000Z","msg":"香港專家大定国內專家大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n醫管局你自己答返啦"},{"pid":"9c1b9f09eaf86fa5845081273eaad893bea4f768","tid":2142191,"uid":37505,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T08:49:29.000Z","msg":"屌，班雪姑柒友識唔識架<br />\n咪撚落到黎呀呀渣渣鳩up當秘笈喎"},{"pid":"3abbf88676325aa250590c568c1182d26575404d","tid":2142191,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T08:56:16.000Z","msg":"支那式政治正確 , 越麻煩代表越準確"},{"pid":"21fda650e6f35fdf2fd409da0fb40500e585027f","tid":2142191,"uid":15815,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T08:58:04.000Z","msg":"西醫:大陸喱 我幾條A入港大讀E架 你識條春咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff72a10e104e5e180017e5d517c99cc6b20feac0","tid":2142191,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T08:59:54.000Z","msg":"單係要伸支棒入鼻窿我諗都嚇窒咗唔少人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"301a17ad6d5431c7c6b4ecdd918ff0d9080fd93e","tid":2142191,"uid":268868,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T09:01:06.000Z","msg":"呢個人 炒得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a7751fd9637e3e53fef0ab7b775160c1b9f8051","tid":2142191,"uid":10890,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T09:17:31.000Z","msg":"屌啲病毒喺個肺部繁殖<br />\n你話deep throat saliva定係nasopharyngeal secretion近啲個肺？<br />\n傻嘅都知越近個肺嘅sample越準啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />